<li id="cite_note-7"><b><a href="#cite_ref-7" title="">^</a></b> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="book" id="CITEREFProse.2C_Francine2006">Prose, Francine (2006). <i><a href="/wiki/Reading_Like_a_Writer" title="Reading Like a Writer">Reading Like a Writer</a> pp.24-25.</i>. HarperCollins. <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/0060777044" class="internal">ISBN 0-06-077704-4</a>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=%5B%5BReading+Like+a+Writer%5D%5D+pp.24-25.&amp;rft.aulast=Prose%2C+Francine&amp;rft.au=Prose%2C+Francine&amp;rft.date=2006&amp;rft.pub=HarperCollins&amp;rft.isbn=0-06-077704-4&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Show,_don%27t_tell"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
